oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Proud Country at the Grand Ole Opry House (20695)

oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (red on brown) announcing the Proud Country, presented by the Association of Country Entertainers, featuring Roy Acuff, Lonzo and Oscar, Grandpa Jones, and others at the Grand Ole Opry House on June 10.
